Anker recently kicked off a new <a href="https://anker.pxf.io/kOx0Kz">Halloween sale</a> with up to 20 percent off the company's most popular charging accessories. Most accessories have had their discounts automatically applied, but you can enter the code halloween2025 at checkout as well to get the discount.<br/>
